com.tngtech.propertyloader.impl
Interface PropertyLoaderFilter

All Known Implementing Classes:
VariableResolvingFilter
public interface PropertyLoaderFilter

Implementations of this interface are used to postprocess properties after raw loading. Examples include variable expansion, warning if keys or values look bad, or de-obfuscating values.

Method Summary
 void filter(OrderedProperties props, PropertyLoaderState state)
          Applies some processing to loaded properties.
 

Method Detail

filter

void filter(OrderedProperties props,
            PropertyLoaderState state)
Applies some processing to loaded properties. Implementations are permitted to modify the given properties in any way, including adding or removing properties. If some unacceptable problem is encountered, should throw InitializationException or an appropriate subclass.
